# Xinjiang Shao

[https://xinjiangshao.com](https://xinjiangshao.com)

Coding by day, conjuring culinary creations by night, Xinjiang Shao is a software engineer who fuels his creativity with an eye for design and a passion for cooking. In his free time, he brings his dreams to life in the kitchen, crafting delicious dishes and seeking out new and imaginative ways to design pleasant things.

